title: Ep. - 231 - Bob Harper From The Biggest Loser and Paige Desorbo from Summer House
description:
Bob Harper is one of the most well-known health and fitness experts in the world, and is host of The Biggest Loser, USA Network’s revamped version of the original hit series. He talks about recovering from a heart attack, this season of the show, preventative health, and his reality television exes. 

 

Paige DeSorbo from Bravo’s Summer House talks about what happens this season, whether she thinks it is odd an engaged couple lives in a Hamptoms share house, and what franchise of Real Housewives needs to be recast. 


 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
